l\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fjy1665702674311.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fjy1665702674311.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fjy1665702674311\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Controls whether DDE support is available within a Uniface application.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fjy1665702674311__topic_d145937e1_d145938e1_d145939e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fjy1665702674311__p_d145940e1_d145941e1_d145942e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DDE</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"fjy1665702674311__section_w3316ab1b5b3_w3317ab1b5_w3318ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fjy1665702674311__table_d17810e1_d17811e1_d17812e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"crc1665702674239.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crc1665702674239.html\" title=\"The [udde] section controls the use of Dynamic Data Exchange (DDE) support from within a Uniface application.\">[udde]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rpv1665702769551.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>DDE Support</a><p>Dynamic Data Exchange (DDE) is an old communication technology that allows DDE-enabled applications running under Microsoft Windows to dynamically exchange data with another via a defined link between them. The communication between such applications is referred to as a conversation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527545\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527545\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "DDE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Controls whether DDE support is available within a Uniface application. DDE = on | off Default value off File section [udde] Related Links DDE Support Dynamic Data Exchange (DDE) is an old communication technology that allows DDE-enabled applications running under Microsoft Windows to dynamically exchange data with another via a defined link between them. The communication between such applications is referred to as a conversation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}